    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Stance)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>While in this stance, any weapon attack made against a single creature (including Armed techniques) deals 1d6 additional damage (not multiplied on critical hits). If you score a critical hit with such an attack, it deals an additional 1d10 bonus damage per multiplier (so 1d10 on x2, 2d10 on x3, etc). This technique applies only to attacks made with a melee weapon appropriately sized for you.</p>\n\n\n\n",
